ican baseball player and coach * 1974 &ndash; [[René Reinumägi]], Estonian actor, director, and screenwriter *[[1975]] &ndash; [[Christopher Barzak]], American author and educator * 1975 &ndash; [[Cara Dillon]], Irish singer-songwriter * 1975 &ndash; [[Ravindra Pushpakumara]], Sri Lankan cricketer * 1975 &ndash; [[Mike Sellers]], American football player *[[1976]] &ndash; [[Jaime Murray]], English actress *[[1977]] &ndash; [[Paul Casey]], English golfer *[[1978]] &ndash; [[Justin Bartha]], American actor * 1978 &ndash; [[Anderson da Silva Gibin]], Brazilian footballer * 1978 &ndash; [[Josh Hartnett]], American actor * 1978 &ndash; [[Julian Huppert]], English academic and politician * 1978 &ndash; [[Damian Marley]], Jamaican singer-songwriter and producer * 1978 &ndash; [[Gary Teale]], Scottish footballer *[[1979]] &ndash; [[David Carr (American football)|David Carr]], American football player * 1979 &ndash; [[Tamika Catchings]], American basketball player * 1979 &ndash; [[Luis Ernesto Michel]], Mexican footballer * 1979 &ndash; [[Andriy Voronin]], Ukrainian footballer *[[1980]] &ndash; [[Justin Griffith]], American football player * 1980 &ndash; [[Sandra Laoura]], French skier * 1980 &ndash; [[CC Sabathia]], American baseball player * 1980 &ndash; [[Yvonne Sampson]], Australian journalist and sportscaster *[[1981]] &ndash; [[Paloma Faith]], English singer-songwriter and actress * 1981 &ndash; [[Anabelle Langlois]], Canadian figure skater * 1981 &ndash; [[Joaquín (footballer)|Joaquín]], Spanish footballer * 1981 &ndash; [[Romeo Santos]], American singer-songwriter * 1981 &ndash; [[Stefan Schumacher]], German cyclist *[[1982]] &ndash; [[Jason Cram]], Australian swimmer * 1982 &ndash; [[Mao Kobayashi (actress)|Mao Kobayashi]], Japanese newscaster and actress (d. 2017) *[[1984]] &ndash; [[Jurrick Juliana]], Dutch footballer * 1984 &ndash; [[Liam Ridgewell]], English footballer * 1985 &ndash; [[Mati Lember]], Estonian footballer * 1985 &ndash; [[Von Wafer]], American bas